Text: Thanks, but original Femjoy pics are around 2Mb per pic. How come these are so small? Also, when you put them in a zip file, people looking for one missing set (collectors as you say) can't see if you have what they're missing.

These are not the HQ scans and are perfect for those who don't have the bandwidth to pull back those.

Another way of looking at it is that this way he and others willing to seed can help others get a full set like you've got instead of just trying to fill some "collector's set". :) P2P isn't the type of place for "What's In It For Me' leechers. ;)

Thanks, Black Moth, always appreciate your posts.
